    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-803d-8543-fc17a617fb74",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper does an overview of the supervised learning algorithms that attempt to predict exam performance of students in both classification and regression scenarios. The empirical results show that the models using engagement and past performance data used as input to an Artificial Neural Network achieve the highest precision. Demographic data does not seem to have a large effect at predicting exam performance.   ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-803d-8543-fc17a617fb74",
